name: "Budgie Gang"
description:
I am a budgie lover, I had three wonderful birds in the past. One of them lived 14 years and he was like a brother to me. Other two lived shorter, but still they are also my brother and sister. I was feeling like no matter how small they are, they were always rebel, crazy and demanding what they want. For example they were going crazy with a little toy, flying over me persistently to eat a fruit which I was eating, a place where was not suitable for them and yet not coming and biting when I try to take them away. So, they were definitely tough.

They were the gang. 
Be afraid...
Be very afraid...
